======================================================================
JOB 0005 :: COBOL PROGRAM - ACCOUNT BALANCE CHECK
======================================================================

       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ACCTBAL.
       AUTHOR. NERD-SCROLL.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT ACCT-IN ASSIGN TO ACCTIN.
           SELECT AUDIT-OUT ASSIGN TO AUDOUT.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  ACCT-IN.
       01  ACCT-REC.
           05 ACCT-NO              PIC X(12).
           05 ACCT-TYPE            PIC X(02).
           05 ACCT-BALANCE         PIC S9(9)V99 COMP-3.

       FD  AUDIT-OUT.
       01  AUDIT-REC               PIC X(132).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-COUNT                PIC 9(09) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-TOTAL                PIC S9(11)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-DISPLAY-TOTAL        PIC -ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZ9.99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           OPEN INPUT ACCT-IN
                OUTPUT AUDIT-OUT
           PERFORM UNTIL 1 = 2
              READ ACCT-IN
                 AT END EXIT PERFORM
                 NOT AT END
                    ADD 1 TO WS-COUNT
                    ADD ACCT-BALANCE TO WS-TOTAL
              END-READ
           END-PERFORM
           MOVE WS-TOTAL TO WS-DISPLAY-TOTAL
           DISPLAY 'ACCOUNTS READ: ' WS-COUNT
           DISPLAY 'TOTAL BALANCE: ' WS-DISPLAY-TOTAL
           CLOSE ACCT-IN AUDIT-OUT
           GOBACK.

[COBOL] source member ACCTBAL displayed
